<p>To add this web app to your home screen from Microsoft Edge on Android:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Tap the menu button.</li>
  <li>From the menu, select "Add to phone".</li>
  <li>Review the app name and icon, and then tap "Add" or "Install".</li>
  <li>The Joy of Rails icon will now be added to your home screen.</li>
</ol>
<p>Now you can access the web app by tapping the icon on your home screen.</p>
